title: Klinsmann starts veterans for Confed Cup playoff vs Mexico (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,191 Klinsmann starts veterans for Confed Cup playoff vs Mexico (Yahoo Sports) PASADENA, Calif. (AP) -- Matt Besler and Geoff Cameron are starting in central defense for the United States in their playoff against Mexico on Saturday night to determine a berth in the 2017 Confederations Cup.
